## 🚀 How to Use

### Starting Point
1. Read **QUICK_REFERENCE.md** (2 min) for overview
2. Read **SETUP.md** (5 min) for setup instructions

### Running Tests
```powershell
# 1. Start PostgreSQL
docker run --name postgres-utb-minute -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=postgres -p 5432:5432 -d postgres:latest

# 2. Create test database
docker exec postgres-utb-minute psql -U postgres -c "CREATE DATABASE utb_minute_test;"

# 3. Run all tests
dotnet test UTB.Minute.WebApi.Tests
```

### Expected Output
```
Test summary: total: 31; failed: 0; succeeded: 31; skipped: 0; duration: X.XXs
